{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 About\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\i MIDI LFO Trigger} is a JSFX plugin that creates a linear LFO every time a MIDI note is sent. The LFO is sent to the hidden "Output" slider.\par}
}

